      <div class="leftContentBriefContent">
        <p>Around the 1890s the people of the US first experienced an E-bike. Though.the design of e-bikes was made hundreds of times. But these bikes took a long time to hit the official US market. However, the latest model of an e-bike is inspired by the 1989 model. That model first showed an e-bike with pedal assistance.</p>
        <p>Nowadays. Many experts have innovated excellent e-bike designs. So. modern e-bikes have come a long way from that old model, People love these speedy bikes, But, e-bikes are divided into three categories (in the US) So you should learn more about all these classes before <a href="/collections/all-bikes">buying an e-bike.</a></p>
      </div>
